subject: Re: Are you ready to received your
body:
Dear Mr. Peter Iwu,

Thank you for your email. However, I must inform you that I am not expecting any ATM card from the Federal Government of Nigeria. 

I would advise you to double-check your records and ensure that this message is intended for me.

Best wishes,
Blanche
